Interface BrokerServerIF

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BrokerRMIServerIF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BrokerLocalServer, BrokerRMIServer, BrokerServer

    public interface BrokerServerIF
    The BrokerServerIF interface defines the APIs implementation requirements for all the servers in the application.
